set autoindent
set tabstop=4
set relativenumber
set background=light
set number
colorscheme peachpuff

"Keymaps for C Files

autocmd FileType c inoremap ;p printf("", );<Esc>jjjji
autocmd FileType c inoremap { {<Enter><C-I><Enter>}<Esc>0xkA
autocmd FileType c inoremap ;bp #include<stdio.h><Enter>#include<stdlib.h><Enter><Enter>int main(){<Enter><C-I><Enter>return 0;<Enter>}<Esc>0xkkA
autocmd FileType c inoremap ;for for(<++>; <++>; <++>)<Esc>0i

"General Keymaps
map <Space><Space> /<++><Enter>4x:noh<Enter>i
inoremap <Space><Space> <Esc>/<++><Enter>4x:noh<Enter>i
